xxxx/xx/xx xx:xx:xx : install completed
xxxx/xx/xx xx:xx:xx : copy install into <sandbox>/install
xxxx/xx/xx xx:xx:xx : End Building extenv [default] (master)
EOF

###### should build again since EXTENV_VAR is changed

